# Issue 2 – Missing Certificate Generator

## Symptom

Certificate generation failed.

Command:

```bash
docker compose -f generate-indexer-certs.yml run --rm generator
```

Observed Error:

```text
no such file or directory
```

---

## Root Cause

The cloned repository did not contain:

```text
generate-indexer-certs.yml
```

The repository layout differed from the expected version.

---

## Investigation

Commands used:

```bash
pwd

find . -maxdepth 2 -type f
```

This confirmed that the required file was missing.

---

## Resolution

A clean clone of the correct repository version restored:

```text
generate-indexer-certs.yml

config/certs.yml
```

Certificate generation then completed successfully.

---

## Lesson Learned

Before troubleshooting Docker, verify the repository contents and branch.

