# Issue 4 – Certificate Generation Permission Errors

## Symptom

Certificate generation completed partially.

Observed Errors:

```text
Permission denied

cannot create regular file
```

---

## Investigation

Verified:

* Current working directory
* Mounted folders
* Generated certificate locations

---

## Resolution

Confirmed that the certificate files had been created correctly under:

```text
config/wazuh_indexer_ssl_certs/
```

The deployment continued using the generated certificates.

---

## Lesson Learned

Permission warnings do not always indicate deployment failure.

Always verify the output directory before repeating certificate generation.

